Chris Do and Moismai tackle the controversial truths about personal branding in this candid conversation. They discuss the prevalence of fake personas online, the importance of authenticity, and why self-discovery is at the core of a true personal brand. Learn why 98% of creators fall short and how to build a personal brand rooted in honesty and depth.
